high_descs: Move to the island to the left of you.
Pick up the ladle from the island.
Move to the sink on the other side of the island.
Place the ladle in the sink and run some water before turning off the water and picking up the ladle.
Move to the left of the sink to the counter.
Place the ladle on the counter.
anns.task_desc: Place a cleaned ladle on the counter to the left of the sink.

high_descs: Turn right and head to the island.
Pick up the spoon on the island.
Turn right, head around the island to the left, cross the room, and go to the sink.
Wash the spoon in the sink.
Bring the cleaned spoon to the toaster left of the sink.
Place the cleaned spoon on the counter, in front of the toaster.
anns.task_desc: Put a cleaned spoon on the counter, in front of the toaster.

high_descs: Face to the left.
Pick up the ladle from the end of the kitchen island counter.
Go around the right side of the island to the sink beyond the other end.
Wash the ladle in the sink.
Go to the toaster, on the counter to the left of the sink.
Place the ladle on the counter in front of the toaster.
anns.task_desc: Place a clean ladle on the kitchen counter, in front of the toaster.

high_descs: Turn left toward the ladle on the counter.
Pick up the ladle from the counter top.
Turn right, walk around the right side of the counter top to the sink.
Put the ladle in the sink basin, rinse it off, and take it back out.
Walk left to the toaster on the counter top.
Put the ladle on the counter top, in front of the toaster.
anns.task_desc: Put a clean ladle on a counter top in front of a toaster.

high_descs: Turn to face the counter with the ladle.
Pick the ladle up from the counter.
Cross the room and stand in front of the sink.
Put the ladle in the sink and turn the water on and then off and then pick the ladle up out of the sink.
Move to the left and face the counter to the left.
Put the ladle down on the counter.
anns.task_desc: Put a clean ladle on the counter.

high_descs: Move to the island top the left of you
Pick up the scoop from the island
Move to the sink across the kitchen from you
Clean the scoop in the sink and pick it back up
Move to the counter to the left of the sink
Place the scoop on the counter
anns.task_desc: Put a cleaned scoop on the counter next to the toaster.
